# Use an official Python runtime as a parent image
FROM python:3.8-buster

MAINTAINER Benjamin DONNOT <benjamin.donnot@rte-france.com>

ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND noninteractive

ARG ls_version

# generic install
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y \
    less \
    apt-transport-https \
    build-essential \
    git \
    ssh \
    tar \
    gzip && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*;

# Retrieve Grid2Op
RUN git clone https://github.com/rte-france/Grid2Op

# Install Grid2Op
WORKDIR /Grid2Op
# Use the latest release
RUN git pull
RUN git remote update
RUN git fetch --all --tags
RUN git checkout "tags/v1.7.2" -b "v1.7.2-branch"
# Install Dependencies
RUN pip3 install --no-cache-dir .[optional,challenge]
WORKDIR /

# Make port 80 available to the world outside this container
EXPOSE 80
